         <abstract id="aspace_2336fc1612691e0e4f299dee1d142313">Correspondence, records and printed material of Alliance Française Groupe de New Haven. Correspondents include local officers of Alliance Française, officials of the national Fédération de l'Alliance Française aux États-Unis, and potential lecturers.</abstract>
